{"article_id":"BsGATZVOGsZf7VNj","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Sally Yates :","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"' We believed","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"that Gen. Flynn was compromised '","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"Trump 's former national security adviser could have been blackmailed by the Russians ,","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"Yates tells the Senate .","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"Former acting Attorney General Sally Yates cast a harsh light on the White House on Monday ,","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"detailing","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"how she had informed Trump administration officials","depth":11},{"id":8,"text":"that then-national security adviser Michael Flynn was susceptible to blackmail from Russia ,","depth":11},{"id":9,"text":"only to watch President Donald Trump take 18 days","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"to fire him .","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"\" We believed","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"that Gen. Flynn was compromised , \"","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"she testified at a highly anticipated Senate Judiciary subcommittee hearing .","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"\" To state the obvious ,","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"you don ' t want your national security adviser compromised with the Russians . \"","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"Yates said","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"she warned White House counsel Don McGahn in late January","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"that Flynn , a retired Army lieutenant general , had misled Vice President Mike Pence and other senior officials","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"and that as a result , public statements by White House officials were inaccurate .","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"Yates ' testimony was the first time","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"she has publicly addressed what has become a major controversy for the White House ,","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"given that Trump waited nearly three weeks after Yates ' warning","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"to fire Flynn .","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"By then , it had been reported in the news media","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"that Flynn had misled Pence and other officials","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"when he told them","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"his phone calls with Russia ' s ambassador did not include a discussion of sanctions .","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"Yates said","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"Russia was aware","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"that Flynn had misled his colleagues","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"and could have used that information against him .","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"Democrats seized on this 18-day gap during the hearing ,","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"noting","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"that Flynn was involved in high-level national security decisions ,","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"including new sanctions on Iran ,","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"after the White House had been informed he could be blackmailed .","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"\" Maybe , just maybe , [ Trump ] didn ' t get rid of a guy","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"who lied to the vice president ,","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"who got paid by the Russians ,","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"who went on Russia Today ,","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"because there are other people in his administration","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"who met secretly with the Russians","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"and didn ' t reveal it until later ,","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"until they were caught , \"","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"said Sen. Al Franken","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"( D-Minn. ) .","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"\" That may be why it took him 18 days ,","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"until it became public ,","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"to get rid of Mike Flynn ,","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"who was a danger to this republic . \"","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"Yates ' testimony also followed revelations","depth":4},{"id":52,"text":"that former President Barack Obama had warned Trump against naming Flynn his national security adviser .","depth":4},{"id":53,"text":"Earlier on Monday , Trump launched a preemptive Twitter strike on Yates .","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"He urged lawmakers to ask Yates","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"whether she was responsible","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"for classified information about Flynn ' s conversations with Russia ' s ambassador being leaked to the news media .","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"\" Ask Sally Yates , under oath ,","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"if she knows","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"how classified information got into the newspapers","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"soon after she explained it to W.H .","depth":13},{"id":61,"text":"[ counsel ] , \"","depth":13},{"id":62,"text":"Trump wrote .","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"Yates and former Director of National Intelligence James Clapper ,","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"who testified alongside Yates ,","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"said","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"they did not know","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"how classified information about Flynn ' s conversations with Russia ' s ambassador ended up in The Washington Post .","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"Both also told members of the Senate Judiciary Subcommittee on Crime and Terrorism","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"that they had never leaked classified information to the news media ,","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"nor authorized anyone else to do so .","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"Trump took to Twitter after the hearing","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"to try to claim vindication .","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"\" Sally Yates made the fake media extremely unhappy today -","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"she said nothing but old news ! \"","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"he wrote .","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"\" The Russia-Trump collusion story is a total hoax ,","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"when will this taxpayer funded charade end ? \"","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"After the hearing , subcommittee Chairman Lindsey Graham","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"( R-S.C. )","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"praised Yates ,","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"saying","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"she \" did the right thing \"","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"by taking her concerns about Flynn to the White House .","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"But Graham also said","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"he had no problem with the White House ' s handling of the issue .","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"\" All","depth":14},{"id":87,"text":"I do know","depth":14},{"id":88,"text":"is that Gen. Flynn got fired , \"","depth":13},{"id":89,"text":"he told reporters .","depth":12},{"id":90,"text":"\" To me , that was the responsible way forward .","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"Should it have been 15 days ?","depth":12},{"id":92,"text":"Should it have been one day ?","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"To me , that ' s not a very big concern . \"","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"Yates ' appearance also revived another controversial episode","depth":7},{"id":95,"text":"- her own firing as acting attorney general on Jan. 30 ,","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"which came","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"after she refused to defend Trump ' s first travel ban","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"targeting citizens from several Muslim-majority countries .","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"As she recounted her attempts","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"to warn the White House about Flynn ,","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"her story came to an abrupt end .","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"She told senators","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"she did not know","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"whether the White House took any actions after January","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"to mitigate the problems","depth":13},{"id":106,"text":"she had flagged ,","depth":13},{"id":107,"text":"given that she is no longer with the Justice Department .","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"\" If nothing was done ,","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"then certainly that would be concerning , \"","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"she said .","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"Senate Republicans brought up Yates ' firing several times ,","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"with Texas ' senators","depth":11},{"id":113,"text":"- Republicans John Cornyn and Ted Cruz -","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"pressing her to justify her refusal","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"to defend an order by the president .","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"\" In the over 200 years of the Department of Justice history , are you aware of any instance","depth":11},{"id":117,"text":"in which the Department of Justice has formally approved the legality of a policy","depth":12},{"id":118,"text":"and three days later the attorney general has directed the department not to follow that policy","depth":13},{"id":119,"text":"and to defy that policy ? \"","depth":13},{"id":120,"text":"Cruz asked .","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"\" I ' m not ,","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"but I ' m also not aware of a situation","depth":12},{"id":123,"text":"where the Office of Legal Counsel was advised not to tell the attorney general about it","depth":13},{"id":124,"text":"until after it was over , \"","depth":13},{"id":125,"text":"Yates responded .","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"She said","depth":8},{"id":127,"text":"she learned about the executive order from media reports ,","depth":9},{"id":128,"text":"even though she had met with McGahn earlier that day .","depth":9},{"id":129,"text":"Yates also issued a forceful defense of her decision","depth":8},{"id":130,"text":"to resist the order ,","depth":9},{"id":131,"text":"which was soon blocked by the courts .","depth":9},{"id":132,"text":"\" I did my job the best way","depth":10},{"id":133,"text":"I knew how , \"","depth":10},{"id":134,"text":"she said .","depth":9},{"id":135,"text":"\" I looked at this","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"[ executive order ] ,","depth":11},{"id":137,"text":"I looked at the law ,","depth":11},{"id":138,"text":"I talked with the folks at the Department of Justice ,","depth":12},{"id":139,"text":"gathered them all","depth":13},{"id":140,"text":"to get their views and their input ,","depth":13},{"id":141,"text":"and I did my job . \"","depth":9},{"id":142,"text":"Breaking News Alerts","depth":4},{"id":143,"text":"Get breaking news","depth":7},{"id":144,"text":"when it happens -","depth":7},{"id":145,"text":"in your inbox .","depth":6},{"id":146,"text":"Email Sign Up","depth":7},{"id":147,"text":"By signing up","depth":9},{"id":148,"text":"you agree to receive email newsletters or alerts from .","depth":9},{"id":149,"text":"You can unsubscribe at any time .","depth":8},{"id":150,"text":"This site is protected by reCAPTCHA","depth":7},{"id":151,"text":"and the Google Privacy Policy and Terms of Service apply .","depth":7},{"id":152,"text":"Cruz also brought up the Hillary Clinton email scandal ,","depth":5},{"id":153,"text":"asking Clapper what he would have done","depth":6},{"id":154,"text":"if someone","depth":9},{"id":155,"text":"who worked for him","depth":9},{"id":156,"text":"was forwarding emails to a non-government employee \" spouse \"","depth":8},{"id":157,"text":"- a clear reference to Clinton aide Huma Abedin and her husband , former Rep. Anthony Weiner .","depth":7},{"id":158,"text":"\" It raises all kinds of potential security concerns , \"","depth":5},{"id":159,"text":"Clapper said in response to Cruz ' s hypothetical .","depth":5},{"id":160,"text":"Yates was first scheduled to appear in March before the House Intelligence Committee ,","depth":5},{"id":161,"text":"but the session was canceled","depth":6},{"id":162,"text":"as relations broke down between Intelligence Chairman Devin Nunes","depth":9},{"id":163,"text":"( R-Calif. )","depth":9},{"id":164,"text":"and his committee ' s Democrats ,","depth":8},{"id":165,"text":"who accused him of using his post","depth":8},{"id":166,"text":"to provide political cover for the White House .","depth":8},{"id":167,"text":"The DOJ also raised concerns about Yates ' scheduled appearance before the House panel ,","depth":5},{"id":168,"text":"citing executive privilege .","depth":5},{"id":169,"text":"Into the void stepped Graham ,","depth":6},{"id":170,"text":"whose Judiciary subcommittee has jurisdiction over the FBI and parts of the DOJ .","depth":6},{"id":171,"text":"Graham is a staunch Russia hawk","depth":7},{"id":172,"text":"who has been one of the president ' s fiercest Republican critics .","depth":7},{"id":173,"text":"He has vowed to get to the bottom of Russia ' s meddling in the presidential election and any Trump campaign ties to Moscow .","depth":6},{"id":174,"text":"Graham said last week","depth":5},{"id":175,"text":"the White House raised no objections to Monday ' s hearing with Yates .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":351,"left":317,"right":350,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":317,"left":226,"right":316,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":226,"left":180,"right":225,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":180,"left":178,"right":179,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":178,"left":0,"right":177,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":177,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":179,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":225,"left":211,"right":224,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":211,"left":194,"right":210,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":194,"left":190,"right":193,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":190,"left":185,"right":189,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":185,"left":5,"right":184,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":184,"left":182,"right":183,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":182,"left":6,"right":181,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":181,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":183,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":189,"left":187,"right":188,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":187,"